Text:
It seems I can't even get the download started... I'll keep trying though, and seed for a long while when I'm done.

This album is great and is highly recommended to anyone who likes some semi-electronic indie-rock. (Radiohead --- Kid A, Amnesiac, Hail to the Thief --- comes to mind at times, but without VETO sounding like ripoffs or anything like that.) Enjoy!

Hmm, I've been trying to download this since a couple of minutes after you posted it and not a single byte has been transfered in my direction... I'm beginning to suspect there's something wrong somewhere...
Right now the official BitTorrent client (for Linux) says that I'm "connected to 5 peers with an average of 19.8% completed (total speed 0 kB/s); connected to 0 seeds; also seeing 0.991 distributed copies"...
Doesn't it seem kinda odd, that it doesn't download anything? Other torrents work just fine.

I am still trying to seed this torrent. Seemed there was some trouble with Bitlord, so I switched to BitTornado, I hope it works now. I will still be seeding as much as I possibly can. Sorry for the inconvenience.
